      • visitParameterizedType

        protected @Nullable Void visitParameterizedType(AnnotatedTypeMirror.AnnotatedDeclaredType type,
                                    ParameterizedTypeTree tree)
        Checks that the annotations on the type arguments supplied to a type or a method invocation are within the bounds of the type variables as declared, and issues the "generic.argument.invalid" error if they are not. This method used to be visitParameterizedType, which incorrectly handles the main annotation on generic types.
